{"id":476903,"date":[{"year":1966,"month":6,"day":30}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"工农兵纪念“七一”诗画选,歌唱共产党　歌唱毛主席","genre":"","count":"274","ytitle":"","mtitle":"歌颂中国共产党","ftitle":"","authors":["胡永槐"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海汽轮机厂　胡永槐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"松柏万年青，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳万代红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的中国共产党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民把您来歌颂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有您的英明领导，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们敢于斗争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拨开乌云见太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命路上力无穷!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有您的正确指引，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们敢于胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快马加鞭换新天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三面红旗舞东风!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举毛泽东思想红旗向前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国建设富强又繁荣!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"松柏万年青，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳万代红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的中国共产党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民把您来歌颂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有您的英明领导，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们胸怀祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大寨红花遍地开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大庆石油如潮涌!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有您的正确指引，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们放眼世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举马列主义大旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横扫一切害人虫!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想光辉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照亮了全世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定叫全球一片红!"}]}